Here is the full **testsmells.org 19-smell academic catalog audit** for `OrderProcessorTests.cs`.

---

## Summary Dashboard

| Severity | Smell Count | Affected Tests |
|----------|-------------|----------------|
| High     | 4           | 4              |
| Medium   | 5           | 4              |
